OL,3,CDad raises millions for charity after
OL,4,Cbeing diagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FCraig Maxwell who has raised more than
OL,7,Fa million pounds to help improve and
OL,8,Fdevelop cancer care in Wales is one of
OL,9,Ffour nominees for the Wales Pride of
OL,10,FBritain fundraiser of the Year Award.
OL,12,FThe 42-year-old father-of-two from
OL,13,FPenarth, Vale of Glamorgan, was given
OL,14,Fmonths to live after being diagnosed
OL,15,Fwith terminal cancer.
OL,17,FHe decided he would do everything he
OL,18,Fcould in his limited time to improve
OL,19,Fcancer diagnosis in Wales.
