OL,3,CDad raises millions for charity after
OL,4,Cbeing diagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FFor Craig, doctors first identified a
OL,7,Ftumour in June 2022 but it took 72
OL,8,Fdays for the official cancer diagnosis
OL,9,Fto come back. Craig decided to do
OL,10,Feverything he could in his limited
OL,11,Ftime to change that.
OL,13,FSo far he has raised over #1.4 million
OL,14,Fthrough a series of fundraising
OL,15,Fchallenges which have included walking
OL,16,F780 miles from Anglesey to Cardiff,
OL,17,Ffollowing the coastline of Wales.
