OL,3,CDad raises millions for charity after
OL,4,Cbeing diagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FThrough the Maxwell Family Fund the
OL,7,Fmoney raised is for the Velindre
OL,8,FCancer Centre to enhance, improve and
OL,9,Fdevelop the cancer pathway in Wales.
OL,11,FThe walk along the Welsh coastline was
OL,12,Fachieved in 26 days to mirror the
OL,13,FQuicDNA Project, a genomics research
OL,14,Fproject to reduce diagnosis time for
OL,15,Flung cancer patients to a maximum of
OL,16,F26 days.
