OL,3,CDad raises millions for charity after
OL,4,Cbeing diagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FCraig, formerly chief commercial
OL,7,Fofficer for the Six Nations rugby
OL,8,Ftournament said: "No father should
OL,9,Fhave to tell their children what I had
OL,10,Fto tell my children.
OL,12,F"And that was the hardest moment me
OL,13,Fand my wife ever had, telling them
OL,14,Fthat I've got limited time with them
OL,15,Fand that I'm going to make the best of
OL,16,Fwhat we can.
