OL,3,CDad raises millions for charity after
OL,4,Cbeing diagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,F"After about two or three weeks of
OL,7,Fstarting my treatments, I managed to
OL,8,Fget myself together and I thought, you
OL,9,Fknow, I want to make a difference
OL,10,Fhere. I thought 78 days to diagnose
OL,11,Fcancer can't be right. We must do more
OL,12,Fto help improve that process, do more
OL,13,Fto give better technology to the
OL,14,Fdoctors and nurses as well."
OL,16,FSpeaking of the walk he said, "The
OL,17,Fsupport I had was just unbelievable.
OL,18,FAnd then to have the support of the
OL,19,Frugby world through the six nations
OL,20,FWelsh Rugby Union, you know, it's just
OL,21,Fbeen incredible."
